# ClassiTranspose — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local for local overrides (never commit .env.local)

# ── HQ SoundFont URL ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The GeneralUser GS SF2 file (~31 MB) is excluded from the Git repo.
#
# For local development:
#   Place GeneralUser-GS.sf2 in public/soundfonts/ and leave this variable unset.
#   The app will fall back to /soundfonts/GeneralUser-GS.sf2 automatically.
#
# For production (Vercel):
#   Host the SF2 on an external CDN (e.g. Cloudflare R2, AWS S3, or similar)
#   and set this variable in the Vercel dashboard → Project → Settings → Env Vars.
#
# VITE_HQ_SOUNDFONT_URL=https://your-cdn.example.com/GeneralUser-GS.sf2
